headline: TE Connectivity announces pricing of €500 million 2.500% senior notes offering
summary: TE Connectivity plc (NYSE: TEL) ("TE Connectivity") today announced that Tyco Electronics Group S.A. ("TEGSA"), its indirect wholly-owned subsidiary, has priced an offering of €500 million aggregate principal amount of its 2.500% senior notes due 2028.
